; Re-exports the ggml C API from GgmlOps.dll so the managed TensorSharp.Backends.GGML
; layer can build ggml compute graphs directly via P/Invoke (see Interop/GgmlApi.cs).
; ggml is statically linked into GgmlOps, so its GGML_API symbols are not exported
; unless listed here. Generated from ExternalProjects/ggml/include/*.h intersected
; with the symbols defined in the built ggml static libraries.
